    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n  (** ** Constant functor from any terminal category *)\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition from_terminal `{Funext} `{@IsTerminalCategory one Hone Hone'}\n             (c : PreCategory)\n  : Pseudofunctor one.",
